{"word":"μετέχω","slug":"μετέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μετέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μετά\">μετά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] ‘have a part in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of enjoying a share of material reward for labor <b>have share in <a href='B:530 9:10'>1 Cor 9:10</a>, <a href='B:530 9:12'>12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of sharing communally <b>partake of:</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on food <b><a href='B:530 10:17'>1 Cor 10:17</a>, <a href='B:530 10:21'>21</a>, <a href='B:530 10:30'>30</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> <b><a href='B:650 5:13'>Hb 5:13</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on sharing human experience <b><a href='B:650 2:14'>2:14</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on being a participant in tribal membership <b><a href='B:650 7:13'>7:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μετέπειτα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μετεωρίζομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}